One of the spokespersons for the Bola Tinubu, Kashim Shettima Presidential Campaign Council, Femi Fani-Kayode, has insisted his candidate will prevail and emerge as president in the forthcoming presidential election. Fani-Kayode disclosed this in a post via his verified Twitter handle on Wednesday. His statement is coming on the heels of the controversies surrounding the Naira redesign policy by the Central Bank of Nigeria, CBN. The former Minister of Aviation said Tinubu remains undeterred by whatever is thrown against him. He wrote, “No matter what is thrown our way, we shall prevail & BAT shall be President. We are bold, strong & undeterred.We have been to the top of the mountain & seen the Promise Land. We shall not just see it but also enter it. It shall be a new era of peace & prosperity.Glory to Nigeria!”